@{U}5  Note for Programmers                                          zView@{u}

There is a very useful GCC library to use zView's @{"codecs" LINK "Codec"}. The library
enables you to load, convert to screen format and zoom a picture with
only one line. To use this library, you need GCC 2.95 or better (a
complete documentation is included).

You can download it from the.zorro.free.fr./misc.html. Updated
versions of the source code can be found on z-tools.sourceforge.net.

@endnode


