@line 1 18 0 0 7
                   used by almost all graphics programs:
                   - 1-, 4-, 8- and 24-bit
                   BMP Version 3 (Microsoft Windows NT):
                   - 16- and 32-bit (not all bits are used)
                   BMP Version 4 (Microsoft Windows 95), which is
